{"tid":486637,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"料千億埋單　沙中綫必超支","createTime":"2017-12-02T04:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T04:37:02.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"37c0827ec2ae284f2ad0a8ff86117cdb09652457","tid":486637,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171202/large/18331044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171202%2Flarge%2F18331044.jpg&h=4e87e33a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■馬時亨<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵主席馬時亨承認，造價798億元的沙中綫定必超支，具體數目會在本月提交政府。立法會議員料沙中綫要近千億「埋單」，要求政府對造價封頂，否則立法會不會通過追加撥款。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>議員：不封頂不通過撥款</strong><br />\n<br />\n馬時亨昨出席活動時指，「（沙中綫）超支係肯定，好多因素唔係港鐵可以控制，包括考古、遲交工地情況」，但他拒透露超支金額。立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會昨討論沙中綫進度，港鐵工程總監黃唯銘被議員多次追問超支金額，他只稱估算已到尾聲，正盡量壓縮成本，結果聖誕前後會提交政府。<br />\n<br />\n委員會主席田北辰自行估算，土瓜灣考古及金鐘站工程共超支50億元，而通脹等因素令成本上升一成，即約80億元，加上灣仔填海發現疑似添馬艦殘骸、分域街地盤要移除地下鋼管及會展站工程改動等額外增70億元，料整體超支100至200億元，令造價增至近千億元。他要求政府參考高鐵超支做法，對沙中綫造價封頂，否則立會不會通過追加撥款。<br />\n<br />\n小組委員會亦討論高鐵進展。民主黨林卓廷關注高鐵啟用時長途車可直達內地城市數目，由前局長鄭汝樺至張炳良都指是16個，現減至10個，質疑內地走數。運房局長陳帆表示，16個只屬顧問建議，由於內地高鐵網繁忙，經與國家鐵路總公司商討，目前可落實10個城市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171202/20232181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232181&d=GAyoW2IVBjKVGnhFwJyaoHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=f8824f7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232181&h=865e89ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171202/20232181</a>"},{"pid":"afb4d871b01f9584f88edcc63b6421158fec5ee3","tid":486637,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de386fa6c4779e68a1f557f3bb908215a9405b55","tid":486637,"uid":85659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong (x<br />\n<br />\nA.T.M. #連鬼佬也會笑的諺稱<br />\n<br />\nASIA Trifle Mechanical"},{"pid":"e9dfc33a7d7b102fffc7948a4b5c6e3884a042cb","tid":486637,"uid":127788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa226c8ea62a6654b1cc2b6f919e0a8550b0453","tid":486637,"uid":129225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:53:20.000Z","msg":"過千億工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5e74108d00dae1932f87bdd47809e84709afad","tid":486637,"uid":161061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要千幾億先埋到單？"},{"pid":"f94e6bf2e36e0558bca80e5d189735ec82c13630","tid":486637,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:08:40.000Z","msg":"十年前港豬支持兩鐵合併，所以要支持埋呢d超支架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正大部分港豬都鐘意奶港鐵鞋底"},{"pid":"6294ec007a9eff76635a655032a8fd1363fcebc7","tid":486637,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12